    <item>
      <title>房地产危机和经济放缓致中国抗议活动增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/china-s-economic-malaise-stirs-rising-protests-on-labor-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济放缓令民众感到不安，且北京方面不愿采取更大胆的措施来促进经济增长，中国的抗议活动正在增多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/china-s-economic-malaise-stirs-rising-protests-on-labor-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 04:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
